description: Provides a list of Call Analytics jobs that match the specified criteria. If no criteria are specified, all Call Analytics jobs are returned. To get detailed information about a specific Call Analytics job, use the operation.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: Lists all Call Analytics jobs that have the status specified in your request. Jobs are ordered by creation date, with the newest job first.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If NextToken is present in your response, it indicates that not all results are displayed. To view the next set of results, copy the string associated with the NextToken parameter in your results output, then run your request again including NextToken with the value of the copied string. Repeat as needed to view all your results.

nested_items.name: CallAnalyticsJobSummaries
nested_items.description: Provides a summary of information about each result.

nested_items.name: CallAnalyticsJobName
nested_items.description: The name of the Call Analytics job. Job names are case sensitive and must be unique within an Amazon Web Services account.

nested_items.name: CreationTime
nested_items.description: The date and time the specified Call Analytics job request was made.

nested_items.name: StartTime
nested_items.description: The date and time your Call Analytics job began processing.

nested_items.name: CompletionTime
nested_items.description: The date and time the specified Call Analytics job finished processing.

nested_items.name: LanguageCode
nested_items.description: The language code used to create your Call Analytics transcription.

nested_items.name: CallAnalyticsJobStatus
nested_items.description: Provides the status of your Call Analytics job.

nested_items.name: CallAnalyticsJobDetails
nested_items.description: Provides detailed information about a call analytics job, including information about skipped analytics features.

nested_items.name: Skipped
nested_items.description: Contains information about any skipped analytics features during the analysis of a call analytics job.

nested_items.name: Feature
nested_items.description: Indicates the type of analytics feature that was skipped during the analysis of a call analytics job.

nested_items.name: ReasonCode
nested_items.description: Provides a code indicating the reason why a specific analytics feature was skipped during the analysis of a call analytics job.

nested_items.name: Message
nested_items.description: Contains additional information or a message explaining why a specific analytics feature was skipped during the analysis of a call analytics job.

nested_items.name: FailureReason
nested_items.description: If CallAnalyticsJobStatus is FAILED, FailureReason contains information about why the Call Analytics job failed. See also: Common Errors.
